narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Good chance to practice oral English and learn how to be TA
The course requires lots of engagement, which is good

Strengths are that this course covers English pronunciation, presentation, vocabulary and teaching skills, enabling us to have a comprehensive understanding of the requirements of good teaching. Weakness of the course is that there are many students taking the course at the same time so that one student has limited time for discussion and presentation.
